Sometimes, It feels like this is just the end of perfection. Nothing can be better than this masterpiece of Coke Studio.But Coke Studio just shatters your perception bringing out a new gem with each and every release.It is unbelievable how it puts such sparkling talent, beauty, culture, folk and musical melody of Pakistan in a steady flow that just takes you in a magical world . Literally, you guys have made me fall short of words which may actually define your talent, beauty and splendor.The only possible way left to narrate your matchless class is the fact that each and every masterpiece of CS makes me hate Donald Trump more than before Lol :D...
Keep rocking Pakistan, You will rise and rock the world.Best wishes and blessings for you.
Love and respect from USA
